380
00:15:10,161 --> 00:15:11,460
You were right, Matt!

381
00:15:11,620 --> 00:15:12,620
How did you know?

382
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:14,820
I kind of went through the same thing
myself.

383
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,200
Welcome back!

384
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:19,880
